<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>SCP-CN-1964</strong> - 橱柜里的骷髅<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fisher-yu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5018779); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5018779&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663941" alt="Fisher Yu" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5018779)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fisher-yu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5018779); return false;">Fisher Yu</a></span></p>
<p>Site-CN-34发生了什么？</p>
<p><a href="/fisher">点此进入作者页</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
